### 4.1 Prompt Engineering

In this project, Large Language Models (LLMs) are guided using carefully designed prompts.  
The prompt defines the age of the child, preferred language, cultural context, and the moral value to be conveyed.  
A well-structured prompt ensures that the generated story is age-appropriate, culturally rich, and morally meaningful.

